    "Connected firmware doesn't support renaming. Update firmware.": {
      "comment": "DeviceRenameView footer caption shown when the connected firmware lacks CHR_DEVICE_NAME (older builds). Rendered in orange.",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "接続中のファームウェアは名前変更に未対応です。ファームウェアを更新してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Connected firmware doesn't support the OSD layout characteristic. Alignment and show/hide still work; vertical position will not.": {
      "comment": "OSD layout editor preview footnote shown when older firmware lacks CHR_OSD_LAYOUT.",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "接続中のファームウェアは OSD レイアウト機能に未対応です。配置と表示／非表示は動きますが、縦位置の調整は反映されません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Controls": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "コントロール"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Couldn't broadcast the bind packet. The M5Stick switched to a fresh pairing but your goggle wasn't notified — use Restore previous goggle.": {
      "comment": "PairingSettingsView error label for the New-Pairing case where the local UID was committed but the ESP-NOW bind broadcast didn't go out, leaving the goggle on the old UID.",
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "バインドパケットを送信できませんでした。M5Stick は新しいペアリングに切り替わりましたが、ゴーグルには通知できていません — 「前のゴーグルに戻す」を使ってください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Couldn't restore the previous pairing — the M5Stick may have disconnected. Try again.": {
      "comment": "PairingSettingsView error label for the recovery-path failure case (the second-chance restore broadcast also didn't go through).",
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "前のペアリングを復元できませんでした — M5Stick が切断された可能性があります。もう一度試してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
