    "This permanently removes every saved race.": {},
    "This permanently removes this saved race.": {},
    "This switches the M5Stick to a fresh pairing ID and broadcasts it to your goggle in one step.\n\nMake sure your goggle is in bind mode (ELRS menu → Bind) BEFORE tapping Apply, otherwise the goggle won't pick up the new pairing.\n\nIf your goggle's backpack was flashed with a fixed bind phrase, the goggle will silently revert to that on its next reboot — use Restore previous goggle to get lap times back.\n\nCurrent pairing: %@": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "M5Stick を新しいペアリング ID に切り替え、その ID を一度の操作でゴーグルへブロードキャストします。\n\n「適用」をタップする前に、ゴーグルがバインドモード(ELRS メニュー → Bind)になっていることを必ず確認してください。そうしないと、ゴーグルは新しいペアリングを受け取りません。\n\nゴーグルのバックパックが固定のバインドフレーズで書き込まれている場合、再起動後は静かにそのフレーズへ戻ります — その場合は「前のゴーグルに戻す」でラップタイムを復帰できます。\n\n現在のペアリング: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Time": {
      "comment": "OSD layout editor Show-rows toggle label for row 0 (time-left countdown).",
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "残り時間"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Time Attack · %@s": {},
    "Tip: install Kyoko / Otoya / O-ren Enhanced from iOS Settings → Accessibility → Spoken Content → Voices for noticeably better quality.": {
      "comment": "Japanese-specific nudge in Audio settings — recommends Enhanced voices instead of the locked Siri voices.",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ヒント: 設定 → アクセシビリティ → 読み上げコンテンツ → 声 から Kyoko / Otoya / O-ren (Enhanced) をインストールすると音質が大幅に向上します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Top row": {
      "comment": "OSD layout editor: row label paired with the slider that picks the top row of the visible OSD block.",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上端の行"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Top row of the visible OSD block on the goggle (1-indexed). The block is as tall as the number of visible rows; the slider's range adapts so the block never falls off the bottom.": {
      "comment": "OSD layout editor Position section footer explaining the slider's behaviour.",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ゴーグルに表示する OSD ブロックの上端の行 (1 始まり)。ブロックの高さは表示する行数と同じで、スライダーの範囲はブロックが下端をはみ出さないよう自動で調整されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Total Time": {},
    "Trend": {},
    "Two reasons this can happen:\n• The app is running outside Xcode's local StoreKit sandbox. Run from Xcode (Cmd+R) to test the paywall against the bundled .storekit config.\n• The App Store Connect products are still in review / Missing Metadata. They have to be approved before they appear in real builds.": {},
